00:58:34,677 --> 00:58:36,668
No, Winston...

655
00:58:39,482 --> 00:58:42,212
Winston, let me...
let me talk to you later, okay?

656
00:58:42,285 --> 00:58:44,549
Can I just... Yeah.

657
00:58:44,621 --> 00:58:47,089
Let me talk to you later.
Please?

658
00:58:47,156 --> 00:58:49,647
Okay? Thanks.
