685
01:03:04,647 --> 01:03:07,582
Uh, no, I... I... I don't have
an animal friend.

686
01:03:07,650 --> 01:03:11,450
I'm an old friend of Carm...
uh, Dr. Markowski's.

687
01:03:11,521 --> 01:03:13,955
Um, Carmen has
a really tight schedule.

688
01:03:14,023 --> 01:03:16,958
She may have a minute,
