689
01:03:17,026 --> 01:03:19,187
Yeah, okay.

690
01:04:22,825 --> 01:04:25,817
<i>No, no, no.</i>
<i>Of course I won't forget you, Cleo.</i>

691
01:04:27,196 --> 01:04:29,130
<i>Yes, I promise.</i>

692
01:04:29,198 --> 01:04:31,632
<i>Thank you,</i>
<i>Dr. Markowski.</i>
<i>Mm-hmm.</i>

693
01:04:31,701 --> 01:04:34,226
- Bye now.
- Bye, Cleo.

694
01:04:34,303 --> 01:04:36,294
See you next week,
Mrs. Dorston.

695
01:04:41,277 --> 01:04:44,940
<i>[Door Closes]</i>
<i>[Footsteps]</i>

696
01:04:46,015 --> 01:04:48,006
